Volumes and Blueprint script can be used together getting the best from both side. Volumes cover the area where it should be loaded or visible for sure. But having scripted event that makes it visible at certain times when it needed. i.e. just before the door opens. (Just to make sure in a real situation like that you would not use glass doors. I just want people to see what happens.)
